{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7434edab5c","title":"给朋友的信：“谭天荣肯定要倒霉”","origin":"《南开大学右派反动言论选集》（天津：南开大学社会主义思想教育教研室，1957年9月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5a5e924fee","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":24,"articleId":"7434edab5c"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"c428c18fac","name":"刘克敬"},{"id":"f2840d39f9","name":"南开大学"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"bf46618a58","type":"title","text":"给朋友的信：“谭天荣肯定要倒霉”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7434edab5c"},{"id":"f93ebfaaa5","type":"authors","text":"南开大学刘克敬","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7434edab5c"},{"id":"fcddf91099","type":"subtitle","text":"[刘克敬：南开大学物理系学生]","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7434edab5c"},{"id":"8580e592bc","type":"appellation","text":"涛：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7434edab5c"},{"id":"3dce50c706","type":"paragraph","text":"来信均接。不再讲了。现在正批判右派。兄等宜多加注意言行，诸事总是小心些为妙，因为生活中别有用心的人大有人在，非君子之思所能尽知小人之心。老兄，生活永远是生活，社会永远是社会。谭天荣肯定要倒霉。我北大的朋友恐亦将倒霉。木偶社能解散就解散吧！（请原谅我的无知之言和最粗暴的干涉）继续存在下去，恐有些麻烦。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7434edab5c"},{"id":"61269d624b","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7434edab5c"},{"id":"d44cb22598","type":"paragraph","text":" 克敬6．24","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7434edab5c"},{"id":"e97401e233","type":"appellation","text":"×：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7434edab5c"},{"id":"f914af1c93","type":"paragraph","text":"来信均接。学校情况知道一些，估计到一些。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7434edab5c"},{"id":"e0fe3b1014","type":"paragraph","text":"我建议：将我们前一时期写的信全部烧掉。（包括这封信在内），并不是我们在信里说了不好的话，而是为了避免麻烦。千万听我的话烧掉。烧一下，不过举手之劳，而不烧，即可能（自然不是一定）带来无限烦恼。为何不烧呢？","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7434edab5c"},{"id":"33cc38cf37","type":"paragraph","text":"请快点来信对我讲一讲：学校几号开学？普通同学（非党团员）几号到校？团员学习几号至几号？","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7434edab5c"},{"id":"e96a367ffc","type":"paragraph","text":"清华开除廿七名团员，北大十六名，我校恐亦在十到廿之间。一切都可能发生。不过，请老兄切记：不管什么情况发生，都应该冷静和乐观。有很多话我现在不讲了。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7434edab5c"},{"id":"55ca811152","type":"paragraph","text":"你的身体应多注意，因此就更不应该激动和生气。岂不闻“山穷水尽疑无路，柳暗花明又一村”吗？无论如何，我们必须生活，不是吗？","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7434edab5c"},{"id":"43d0a76039","type":"paragraph","text":"学斌返校否？在京曾见宗敏否，有何用我处，请告知，我随时可以效劳。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7434edab5c"},{"id":"c56515c353","type":"paragraph","text":"一切面谈。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7434edab5c"},{"id":"8143eac237","type":"paragraph","text":"祝","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7434edab5c"},{"id":"e9f0275928","type":"paragraph","text":"好","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7434edab5c"},{"id":"f2289765a5","type":"paragraph","text":" 克敬8．24","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7434edab5c"},{"id":"da8186cd9b","type":"appellation","text":"×：","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7434edab5c"},{"id":"9276d36855","type":"paragraph","text":"兹寄上×元请马上替我交给学生科。余下所欠之数当于返校时交上，请代为所明。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7434edab5c"},{"id":"4839dbef4f","type":"paragraph","text":"望来信。（收据不要寄了，真是！）","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7434edab5c"},{"id":"ec256c56f4","type":"paragraph","text":"你与学斌来信我已处理完毕。这信亦当烧掉。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7434edab5c"},{"id":"261e99309e","type":"paragraph","text":"索恩正已见报，想既称集团，当更有他人。","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7434edab5c"},{"id":"1c0444d259","type":"paragraph","text":"祝","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7434edab5c"},{"id":"2db37031bb","type":"paragraph","text":"近安","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7434edab5c"},{"id":"21b70c1df1","type":"paragraph","text":" 克敬8．29","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7434edab5c"}],"page":{"id":"d278286ff5","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7434edab5c","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}